    <note>Wang(2) Su [1881] Dan's [8153] son, Yong(1)'s [7091] younger brother, Zhi(1)'s [7079] cousin, Gong's [7084] and Shuo [1870] father, Jing(1)'s [1788] uncle, and Zhen(2)'s [1776] granduncle. Li(2) Wei(3)'s [7042], Teng(1) She's [1610] and Zhang(1) Shixun(1)'s [279] son-in-law and Su(1) Qi's [1490] brother-in-law. Affinal relation of Yan(4) Xun [2068]. Fan(2) Chunren's [559] cousin-in-law. His grandson, Zhen(3) [3947], held minor fiscal offices, including a position in the State Trading Bureau between 1082 and 1086. Zhang Fangping, WJ, 37.34b-42a; XCB, 144.5a, 325.4a, 330.7b, 339.10a-10b, 340.2a, 370.9b; SHY:ZG, 64.50a; SS, 320.6a-7a; Wang Gui, WJ, 58.9a-17a. CBD, 1, 151.</note>
